  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Melee Martial Attack vs PD, 5 Spaces, 1 Bludgeoning and target makes an Agility Save.</p><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target is pulled towards you and Consumed.</p><p>You can’t use this Attack while you have a creature Consumed.</p><p></p><p><strong>While Consumed:</strong> It’s Restrained and takes 1 Corrosion damage at the end of its turns.</p><p><strong>Escape Consume:</strong> Each time you lose 5 HP, you must make a DC 15 Might Save.</p><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The target is vomited into an adjacent Space and is no longer Restrained.</p><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> Use on demand macro to roll the save.</em></p>",
